  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>France Ski Holidays by Rail</h2>
<p>Discover convenience, comfort and unrivalled views on your route to France’s snow capped peaks.</p>
<div class="c-tabs-beta__content-table--row-wrapper">
<p><img src="/media/13062294/italy_the-dolomites-ski-area_selva_mountains-skis.jpg" alt="franceresorts" data-udi="umb://media/746f80f97a1f4c209c1aabb4878f0bb1" /></p>
<h3>Travel by rail to France's premier ski resorts</h3>
<p>Considering a ski holiday in France? There’s no better way to start the adventure than by rail. Arrive at France’s premier ski destinations refreshed and ready. Say goodbye to airport queues and embrace spacious comfort. When the destination is as stunning as the journey, you’re not just travelling but creating memories every step of the way.</p>
<p>Ready to experience a ski holiday by rail? Book online by selecting London St Pancras for departure or <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">contact us</a> to find out more.</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><em>(New 2024/25 train time details coming shortly)</em></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/search-results?/search-results?to=[CH]&amp;from=QQS" target="_blank" title="Rail deals" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?/search-results?to=[CH]&amp;from=QQS">View France Rail Deals</a></p>
